Class CK_C_INITIALIZE_ARGS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.CK_C_INITIALIZE_ARGS

  • public class CK_C_INITIALIZE_ARGS

    Class containing the optional arguments for the C_Initialize function.

    Further information is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
